deck: As ZippyCakes and SnotMuffin train to learn their powers, SnoMuffin summons the bacon loving cupcake, SkullLicker. Meanwhile, in order to raise his Ghoul Army, Lord DeCayer frees dark magic master Big Poppa ThunderButt from his concrete prison.
description:
The Rise of Big Poppa ThunderButt

Issue #2 of ZippyCakes and SnotMuffin introduces us to new friends and foes as the boys learn more about their powers and possibly there lack of. The questions from issue #1 are answered as we witness the "Rise of Big PoppaThunderButt"!
name: The Rise of Big Poppa ThunderButt

description:
Call of The Swine

As if things weren't tough enough for the boys- this issue brings us the "Call of The Swine" which introduces MORE sinister villains. PLUS SnotMuffin has a major cupcake malfunction that soon won't be forgotten!
name: Call of the Swine
